ssure-hamas-netanyahu-picks-a-fight-with-qatar/0000018d-c5b6-d1aa-a78d-edb6c3920000</guid></item><item><title>三名以色列警察被指控性侵犯犯罪嫌疑人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-20/ty-article/.premium/three-israeli-police-officers-accused-of-sexually-assaulting-a-crime-suspect/0000018d-c58d-d20c-a79d-fdcf89c10000</link><description>嫌疑人因涉嫌盗窃汽车而被捕，他向警察局提出投诉，但在寻求法院命令后才接受体检</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 09:12:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-20/ty-article/.premium/three-israeli-police-officers-accused-of-sexually-assaulting-a-crime-suspect/0000018d-c58d-d20c-a79d-fdcf89c10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队宣布加沙战斗中受伤士兵死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-announces-death-of-soldier-wounded-in-gaza-fighting/0000018d-c503-db4d-a5fd-dd2fac5f0000</link><description>22 岁的毛兹·莫雷尔上士上周在加沙地带战斗中受伤，于周二不治身亡</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 07:15:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-announces-death-of-soldier-wounded-in-gaza-fighting/0000018d-c503-db4d-a5fd-dd2fac5f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列希望比巴斯的视频能够向哈马斯施压，但不会加速人质谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-20/ty-article/.premium/israel-hoped-the-bibas-video-would-pressure-hamas-but-it-wont-speed-up-hostage-talks/0000018d-c337-d0dd-adff-d73f4ebf0000</link><description>发布 Shiri Bibas 和她的两个婴儿被绑架的视频可以达到两个目的：鼓励加沙人报告自己的命运，并加大对哈马斯的国际压力，要求其在人质换取停战谈判中更加灵活 ■ 在圣殿山前线与此同时，斋月祈祷危机很有可能以妥协告终</description><pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 04:03:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-20/ty-article/.premium/israel-hoped-the-bibas-video-would-pressure-hamas-but-it-wont-speed-up-hostage-talks/0000018d-c337-d0dd-adff-d73f4ebf0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯领导人哈尼亚和高级官员代表团抵达开罗参加加沙停火谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-20/ty-article-live/idf-concern-for-abducte